---
// One donation iframe for the whole site. transition:persist keeps it alive across in-site
// navigation, so it loads ONCE (in the background, hidden) and is already rendered when the
// Support page opens, with no buffer. CSS keeps it off until a page renders .embed-wrap
// (the Support page), then it is shown filling the area above the navbar.
---
<iframe
  id="zeffy-frame"
  transition:persist="zeffydonateframe"
  title="Donation form powered by Zeffy"
  src="https://www.zeffy.com/embed/donation-form/d-lanthropy"
  allowpaymentrequest
  allowtransparency="true"
  loading="eager"
></iframe>
